OL,7,FFour-time Tour de France champion
OL,8,FChris Froome has been airlifted to
OL,9,Fhospital after a training accident in
OL,10,FFrance left him with a fractured
OL,11,Fvertebrae, collapsed lung and five
OL,12,Fbroken ribs.
OL,14,FThe British cyclist was on a training
OL,15,Fride on Wednesday when the accident
OL,16,Foccurred and was taken by helicopter
OL,17,Fto a hospital in Toulon on the French
OL,18,FRiviera.
