OL,7,FThe 40-year-old is in a stable
OL,8,Fcondition and is set to undergo an
OL,9,Foperation on his back injury on
OL,10,FThursday.
OL,12,FA statement on Froome's official X
OL,13,Fprofile read: "Chris was airlifted to
OL,14,Fhospital in Toulon yesterday following
OL,15,Fa serious training crash (no other
OL,16,Fcyclists or vehicles were involved).
