OL,7,F"Fortunately, Chris is stable and did
OL,8,Fnot sustain any head injuries,
OL,9,Fhowever, scans have confirmed a
OL,10,Fpneumothorax, five broken ribs and a
OL,11,Flumbar vertebrae fracture, for which
OL,12,Fhe will undergo surgery this afternoon.
OL,14,F"We will update on Chris' condition
OL,15,Ffollowing surgery."
