OL,7,FFroome won the Tour de France with
OL,8,FTeam Sky in 2013, 2015, 2016 and 2017,
OL,9,Fand also claimed grand tour titles at
OL,10,Fthe Giro d'Italia and Vuelta a Espana.
OL,11,FHe has been racing with Israel Premier-
OL,12,FTech since 2021.
OL,14,FHe broke his collarbone at the UAE
OL,15,FTour in February and has previously
OL,16,Fhinted that 2025 could be his final
OL,17,Fyear of competitive racing.
